transcript: - These are the new Apple AirTags. You can connect it to your phone so if you lose your keys or something, you can play a sound. (AirTag beeping) Or if you have the iPhone 12, or a phone that is U1 enabled, you'll be able to use precision tracking. I can just walk around my house until I've found my keys. It's here! Here's a few of the accessories that you can get to put your AirTags in. The key chain, a little loop, and the leather loop. These just snap, just like that, and you can pop out (AirTag clanking) your AirTag. And another cool thing, you can customize them with emojis.
